Trichet Says Up to European Governments to Restore Markets

-- B y   E m m a   R o s s - T h o m a s
-- 
2011-09-20T05:50:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-20/trichet-says-up-to-european-governments-to-restore-markets.html
European Central Bank President
Jean-Claude Trichet said it’s up to European governments to
restore debt markets.  “The governments have the responsibility to guarantee
themselves, individually and collectively, financial stability
to restore a more correct functioning of markets,” he said in
an interview with Spanish newspaper Expansion today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Emma Ross-Thomas at 
 erossthomas@bloomberg.net  